@startuml

skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
hide footbox
skinparam lifelineStyle solid
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam defaultFontName "PingFang SC"
skinparam defaultFontSize 18
skinparam actorFontSize 18
skinparam participantFontSize 18
skinparam databaseFontSize 18
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center

actor "User" as USER
participant ":F̲r̲o̲n̲t̲e̲n̲d̲" as FE
participant ":B̲u̲g̲D̲i̲a̲g̲n̲o̲s̲e̲r̲" as BUG
participant ":A̲S̲T̲P̲a̲r̲s̲e̲r̲" as AST

USER -> FE: 查看失败原因
FE -> BUG: diagnose(code, failures)
activate BUG
BUG -> AST: 定位失败函数
activate AST
AST --> BUG: 返回代码片段
deactivate AST
BUG --> FE: 返回诊断结果
deactivate BUG
FE --> USER: 显示根因分析
@enduml
